---
// Small inline pill rendered next to a plugin name wherever a deprecated
// plugin surfaces in public lists or cards. Purely presentational — the
// caller decides when to mount it based on `plugin.deprecated`.
//
// Palette echoes DashboardBanner.astro's warn tokens (warm warning, not
// alarm red) so deprecated plugins read as "slow down" rather than
// "danger". Accessible label is explicit so screen readers don't read
// the chip as a bare word next to the title.
---
<span
  class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-medium border bg-warn-soft text-warn border-warn/35 align-middle"
  aria-label="Deprecated plugin"
>
  Deprecated
</span>
